bookableLocationId.title: bookableLocationId
bookableLocationId.description: The bookable location Id for the Bookable Location closest to or chosen by the user

country.title: country
country.description: The country where the current user is located, used to find locations near to the current user. Must comply with the ISO 3166 alpha 3 standard such as 'USA".

fromDate.title: fromDate
fromDate.description: The first date booking availabilities are/were searched from. It should always be a date in the future and should always be before or equal to the untilDate.

productId.title: productId
productId.description: The productId of the current product to get Booking Availability Slots for.

storeId.title: storeId
storeId.description: The storeId of the current messaging sessions store, typically set by the Store__c field on the messaging session.

untilDate.title: untilDate
untilDate.description: The latest date booking availabilities are/were searched from. It should always be a date in the future and should always be after or equal to the fromDate.
